---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const pageTitle = 'FSA Eligibility - Thyme4Sleep';
const pageDescription = 'Learn how to use your FSA/HSA funds for pediatric sleep consulting services with Thyme4Sleep.';
---

<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-50 to-teal-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light text-brandChar mb-6">FSA & HSA <span class="font-medium">Eligibility</span></h1>
      <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-accent mx-auto mb-8"></div>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Make the most of your healthcare benefits with our FSA/HSA-eligible sleep consulting services.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
        <div class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-light text-brandChar mb-6">Using <span class="font-medium">FSA/HSA</span> for Sleep Consulting</h2>
          <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-700">
            <p class="text-lg mb-6">
              Many families are pleasantly surprised to learn that pediatric sleep consulting services may be eligible for reimbursement through their Flexible Spending Account (FSA) or Health Savings Account (HSA) with a Letter of Medical Necessity (LMN) from your pediatrician, if needed.
            </p>
            
            <div class="bg-brandPeach/10 p-6 rounded-xl mb-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-brandChar mb-4">How It Works</h3>
              <ol class="space-y-4">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-brandPeach text-brandSage font-bold mr-3">1</span>
                  <span>Schedule a free consultation to discuss your child's sleep challenges</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-brandPeach text-brandSage font-bold mr-3">2</span>
                  <span>Request a Letter of Medical Necessity from your pediatrician, if needed</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-brandPeach text-brandSage font-bold mr-3">3</span>
                  <span>We'll provide an itemized receipt with all necessary documentation</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-brandPeach text-brandSage font-bold mr-3">4</span>
                  <span>Submit to your FSA/HSA provider for reimbursement</span>
                </li>
              </ol>
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-light text-brandChar mt-10 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-lg text-brandChar">What is a Letter of Medical Necessity?</h4>
                <p class="mt-2">
                  A Letter of Medical Necessity (LMN) is a document from your pediatrician stating that sleep consulting services are medically necessary for your child's health and well-being. Many FSA/HSA providers require this for reimbursement of sleep consulting services.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-lg text-brandChar">How do I request reimbursement?</h4>
                <p class="mt-2">
                  After completing your sleep consulting package, we'll provide you with an itemized receipt that includes all necessary information for FSA/HSA reimbursement. Simply submit this receipt along with your LMN to your benefits provider.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-lg text-brandChar">Is sleep consulting always covered?</h4>
                <p class="mt-2">
                  Coverage varies by insurance provider and plan. We recommend contacting your FSA/HSA administrator to confirm eligibility before beginning services. We're happy to provide any additional documentation they may require.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-12 bg-brandSage/5 p-6 rounded-xl border border-brandSage/20">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-brandChar mb-4">Ready to Get Started?</h3>
              <p class="mb-6">
                Take the first step toward better sleep for your family. Book a free 15-minute consultation to learn more about our services and how we can help.
              </p>
              <a 
                href="https://thyme4sleep.neetocal.com/meeting-with-georgia-miller-2" 
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 text-base font-bold text-brandSage hover:text-brandSage bg-brandPeach hover:bg-brandPeach/90 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md"
              >
                Book Free Consultation
                <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-brandSage text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Questions About FSA/HSA Coverage?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Our team is here to help you navigate the reimbursement process.
      </p>
      <a 
        href="mailto:georgia@thyme4sleep.com" 
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 text-base font-bold text-brandSage hover:text-brandSage bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md"
      >
        Contact Us
        <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
